{"tid":1085264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國監獄外牆突然倒塌　230囚犯全未趁機逃跑","createTime":"2019-03-31T04:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T05:11:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d96c5ec87cdaa72119b639d3639383807068e8e4","tid":1085264,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎近郊的普瓦西（Poissy），周四（28日）中午有監獄的外牆突然倒塌，但沒有囚犯趁機逃走。<br />\n <br />\n《巴黎人報》報導，這座位於烏爾蘇拉大道（Avenue des Ursulines）的監獄，部分外牆在中午突然倒塌，當時監獄正在進行維修及強化結構工程。事發後，獄方用模板包圍監獄，沒有任何人趁機逃走。<br />\n <br />\n《費加洛報》（Le Figaro）指，普瓦西監獄目前收容近230名囚犯，包括：曾於1975年闖入OPEC（石油輸出國家組織）維也納總部，挾持超過60名人質的恐怖分子、共產主義信徒「豺狼卡洛斯」（Ilich Ram&iacute;rez S&aacute;nchez，本名：桑切斯）。"},{"pid":"d4e7c3fac9f2b941f5931ca34587826707654f9f","tid":1085264,"uid":76776,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"625e6efa46c9149366742976083d871b6b6e4e87","tid":1085264,"uid":202051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有人偷龍轉鳳換左啲重犯出黎"},{"pid":"46cf5611dd2c82515059d5dd3f88b54ebc2c3bbc","tid":1085264,"uid":228963,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3b9c2764f066b2b7adc9b4651d0a958a709f100","tid":1085264,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"支那真係咩都假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n監獄都會倒塌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1bb2bdafc89fb2668cb80d0342ec871b0fc063","tid":1085264,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39b9dcb46e4c3f75dd159e895732e21c1f836fd6","tid":1085264,"uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2FQ9eX.png\" data-